Alpha Wolf

$AW is a memecoin inspired by Alpha Wolf Telegram sticker pack! Each of them has an analogue in the form of an emoji, with which you can express any emotions and feelings.

Alpha Wolf stickerpack uses following emojis: 😂, 😘, 👍, 😨, 👋, 😍, 😭, 😴, 🤷‍♂️, 😒, 😉, 🤔, 👩‍❤️‍👨, 😎, 😮, 🥴, 😡, 🤯, 😈, 🥶, 🥺, 🙅‍♂️, 🕺, 💪, 😫.
